{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01KDJLJPCqGivnA5RQV3nuWb","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Everything is working. Here's a summary of what was done:\n\n**Root cause:** The `es-transform` StatefulSet (which provides the dedicated transform node) was scaled to 0, and two dependent resources were missing that prevented it from coming back:\n- `es-transform-config` ConfigMap — the pod's elasticsearch.yml config mount\n- `es-transform` headless Service — required by the StatefulSet's `serviceName`\n\n**Actions taken:**\n1. Created `es-transform-config` ConfigMap with `node.roles: [transform]`, joining the existing `es-cluster` cluster\n2. Created the `es-transform` headless Service\n3. Scaled `es-transform` StatefulSet back to 1 replica → pod became Ready\n4. Created the `events-by-service` transform (it had failed during precondition because no transform nodes existed)\n5. Started the transform → checkpoint advanced to `1`, processing all 5 seed documents into 2 rollup entries in `app-events-rollup`"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":253,"cache_read_input_tokens":40834,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":253},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"6e8c8a42-3f6a-4533-83bb-158c4c727ce4","uuid":"cb9cb64b-e2d4-4fe9-8716-45c93c05ee4c","request_id":"req_011Ccez7cnTcCTEDUxS24Vz9"}
